title: They actually made this game good!
text:
I started playing in 2018. Everything was alright, there were new countries, it was smooth.

But, in 2020, everything changed. We stopped having new countries, which was the sole reason why I downloaded this game in the first place.

But, all of a sudden, after 5 whole years, we actually got a new country: Ireland! Out of the entire time Iâ€™ve played this game, this is, by far, the best update I have EVER played.

The characters, the boards, the outfits (yes, plural). It was PERFECT.

So now I ask that you continue with this amazing cycle. Two new countries in a row? That would be awesome - maybe you could do Turkey (Istanbul) for Ramadan next!
